DOMAIN SKETCH WITH MANY EXTRA DETAILS :

Note, this is provided as a glossary for the use cases. The use cases should use terminlogy mentioned here.
It extracts a lot of information from the feature list.

Information such as locatino name etc. WILL NOT GO INTO THE DOMAIN MODEL.

This is for use case reference. The domain model is a strict subset of the information provided here.


USER
------
Has a :
	User account

USER ACCOUNT
-------------
Has a : 
	Account Information
	Availability Status
	Contact List 	# List of all contacts the user knows
	Visibility list 	#List of contacts that see the user as available when status is available


ACCOUNT INFORMATION
--------------------
Has a :
	username
	password
	email 

	workplace
	name
	gender
	Avatar


CONTACT
-------
Is a :
	User


CONTACT LIST
------------
Has :
	Contact Groups  # By default a full contact list has one group (implictit) that has all contacts

CONTACT GROUP
--------------
Has :
	Contacts 	# Collection of contacts


VISIBILITY LIST
---------------
Is a :
	Contact List 



NOTIFICATION
------------
Has a:
	Poster 	# creator of the notification
	Receiver List # contacts that recieve the notification
	

POSTER
-------
Is a:
	User

RECIEVER LIST
--------------
Is a :
	Contact List



MEAL NOTIFICATION
------------------
Is a :
	Notification
Has :
	Meal notification Information



MEAL NOTIFICATION INFOMATION
-----------------------------
Has :
	Location
	Duration
	Start time
	End time
	max capacity 	# maximum number of people allowed
	current capacity 	# How many people have accepted
	Custom message
	Additional Information


CAPACITY UPDATE NOTIFCATION   # pushes capacity status (filled or x remaining) to all contacts that recieved the original meal notification.
----------------------------
Is a :
	Meal Notification 


FRIENDS ATTENDING NOTIFICATION 
-------------------------------
Is a :
	Meal Notification
Has : 
	Contact List   # Subset of the contact list, of a contact who recieved the meal notification.


ACCEPTANCE Notification 	# Just to confirm attendance
-----------------------
Is a :
	Meal Notification


CANCELLATION NOTIFICATION 	# Cancelled by the poster or to cancel attendance of a contact.
-------------------------
Is a :
	Meal Notification





